{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_en9gxBzi3LRsiE4viaaPmKgM","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"tool_qWaqYNlqBZaQ20pUy0Eo4Z7p","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Validate TST-001 implementation plan","prompt":"You are a validator agent for ticket TST-001. Your task is to validate the implementation plan at `aidd/docs/plan/TST-001.md` for executability and risk assessment.\n\n## Validation Checklist\n1. **Executability**: Can each task be implemented with the current codebase?\n2. **Dependencies**: Are all dependencies available (Caffeine, WebFlux, etc.)?\n3. **Research alignment**: Does the plan correctly address the research findings?\n4. **Risk assessment**: What are the main risks and how are they mitigated?\n\n## Key Context from Research\n- No Spring Security in classpath - plan correctly uses custom WebFlux filters\n- Zustand (not Redux) for state management\n- SSE already exists - plan extends it (good decision vs WebSocket)\n- X-Profile-Key header auth (not JWT)\n\n## Output\nWrite your validation report to `aidd/docs/plan/TST-001-validation.md` with:\n1. Validation summary (PASS/WARN/FAIL)\n2. Findings - any issues or concerns\n3. Recommendations - specific improvements if needed\n4. Risk register - high/medium/low risks with mitigation\n\nBe thorough but practical. Flag any blockers that would prevent implementation.","subagent_type":"feature-dev-aidd:validator"}}],"model":"kimi-for-coding","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":32770,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available","prompt_tokens":32770,"cached_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e8271fef-d7fa-47ae-9a86-a79be1e8c480","uuid":"d57164d9-292f-47df-87f7-6764751d7e3c"}
