{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_1PL6OXpuvm1RLjSP89JBJSsI","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"tool_28P90Rt8AN3Bt9re6fSA4HUN","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/aidd/docs/plan/TST-001.md","old_string":"## AIDD:RISKS\n\n| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |\n|------|--------|------------|\n| RBAC filter performance | High | Caffeine cache with 5min TTL; async audit logging |\n| Cache stale roles | Medium | Cache invalidation on role change via SSE broadcast |\n| SSE connection drops | Low | Auto-reconnect with exponential backoff in frontend |\n| Missing audit logs | Medium | Async logging with error queue; never block request |\n| Profile service unavailable | High | Circuit breaker pattern; fail-closed (deny access) |","new_string":"## AIDD:RISKS\n\n| Risk ID | Description | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |\n|---------|-------------|-------------|--------|------------|\n| R-001 | Profile service unavailable | Medium | High | Circuit breaker; fail-closed; cache roles |\n| R-002 | Cache stale roles after assignment | Medium | Medium | Cache invalidation on role change; TTL 5min |\n| R-003 | SSE connection memory leak | Low | Medium | Proper cleanup on disconnect; subscriber limits |\n| R-004 | Audit log write failures | Low | Medium | Async logging; error queue; never block request |\n| R-005 | RBAC filter performance degradation | Low | High | Caffeine cache; async audit; P95 target 10ms |\n| R-006 | Breaking change to existing APIs | Low | High | Feature flags; audit-only mode first; rollback |\n| R-007 | Component scan misses RBAC beans | Medium | High | Add to all profile configs; verify on startup |\n| R-008 | Missing profile service integration | High | High | Define contract; implement fallback to local DB |\n\n### Validation-Derived Risks (from TST-001-validation.md)\n\n**R-007: Component Scan Configuration**\nThe application uses profile-based component scanning. The RBAC module needs to be added to ALL profiles or a shared configuration created.\n- **Mitigation**: Create `RbacConfig.java` with `@Profile(\"!test\")` active in all non-test profiles\n\n**R-008: Profile Service Integration**\nThe plan assumes `profileClient.fetchRoles()` exists, but no backend API for fetching profile roles was found in research.\n- **Mitigation**: Define profile service contract or implement local role storage via `rbac_profile_roles` table"}}],"model":"kimi-for-coding","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":42822,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available","prompt_tokens":42822,"cached_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e8271fef-d7fa-47ae-9a86-a79be1e8c480","uuid":"ff01e1b3-2e72-4aee-b08d-0083505fb062"}
